INSERT INTO `article` VALUES (1,'测试文章','生活随笔','2025-11-23 16:29:13','5',666,12,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560942485-b2a11cc13456?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80','awdawdawdawdwa','[\'tag1\',\'tag2\']',1,'这是一个测试文章'),(3,'Vue3 + Spring Boot 博客开发实战（测试文章）','寄术笔记','2025-11-30 21:39:15','3',3,3,'https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.zmCAiA-sxQrG5bNYz8M8OgHaDy?w=339&h=178&c=7&r=0&o=7&pid=1.7&rm=3','<h2>Vue3 + Spring Boot 博客开发实战</h2>\n\n<p>在现代Web开发中，前后端分离架构已经成为主流。本文将详细介绍如何使用Vue3和Spring Boot构建一个功能完整的个人博客系统，包括前端组件设计、后端接口开发以及数据库设计等关键环节。</p>\n\n<h3>一、技术栈选择</h3>\n\n<p>选择合适的技术栈是项目成功的关键：</p>\n\n<ul>\n    <li><strong>前端</strong>：Vue3、Vite、Pinia、Vue Router、Axios</li>\n    <li><strong>后端</strong>：Spring Boot 3.x、Spring Data JPA、Spring Security</li>\n    <li><strong>数据库</strong>：MySQL 8.0</li>\n    <li><strong>其他工具</strong>：wangEditor、highlight.js、Docker</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>二、核心功能实现</h3>\n\n<h4>2.1 文章管理模块</h4>\n\n<p>文章管理是博客系统的核心功能，主要包括：</p>\n\n<ol>\n    <li>文章的增删改查</li>\n    <li>富文本编辑器集成</li>\n    <li>文章分类与标签管理</li>\n    <li>文章搜索功能</li>\n</ol>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>好的代码是它自己最好的文档。当你考虑要添加一个注释时，先尝试重构代码，让它更清晰。 —— Martin Fowler</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<h4>2.2 前端组件设计</h4>\n\n<p>以下是Vue3组件的示例代码：</p>\n\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&lt;template&gt;\n  &lt;div class=\"article-list\"&gt;\n    &lt;article-item \n      v-for=\"article in articles\" \n      :key=\"article.id\" \n      :article=\"article\" \n      @click=\"viewArticle(article.id)\"\n    /&gt;\n  &lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/template&gt;\n\n&lt;script setup&gt;\nimport { ref, onMounted } from \'vue\'\nimport ArticleItem from \'./ArticleItem.vue\'\nimport { fetchArticles } from \'@/api/article\'\n\nconst articles = ref([])\n\nonMounted(async () =&gt; {\n  articles.value = await fetchArticles()\n})\n\nconst viewArticle = (id) =&gt; {\n  router.push(`/article/${id}`)\n}\n&lt;/script&gt;\n</code></pre>\n\n<h4>2.3 后端接口开发</h4>\n\n<p>Spring Boot控制器示例：</p>\n\n<pre><code class=\"language-java\">@RestController\n@RequestMapping(\"/api/articles\")\npublic class ArticleController {\n    \n    @Autowired\n    private ArticleService articleService;\n    \n    @GetMapping\n    public ResponseEntity&lt;Page&lt;ArticleDTO&gt;&gt; getArticles(\n            @RequestParam(defaultValue = \"0\") int page,\n            @RequestParam(defaultValue = \"10\") int size) {\n        return ResponseEntity.ok(articleService.findArticles(page, size));\n    }\n    \n    @PostMapping\n    public ResponseEntity&lt;ArticleDTO&gt; createArticle(@Valid @RequestBody ArticleRequest request) {\n        return ResponseEntity.status(HttpStatus.CREATED)\n                .body(articleService.createArticle(request));\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<h3>三、数据库设计</h3>\n\n<p>博客系统的主要数据表设计：</p>\n\n<table>\n    <thead>\n        <tr>\n            <th>表名</th>\n            <th>主要字段</th>\n            <th>说明</th>\n        </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n        <tr>\n            <td>blog_article</td>\n            <td>id, title, content, create_time, update_time</td>\n            <td>文章表</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>blog_category</td>\n            <td>id, name, description</td>\n            <td>分类表</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>blog_tag</td>\n            <td>id, name, count</td>\n            <td>标签表</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>blog_user</td>\n            <td>id, username, email, password</td>\n            <td>用户表</td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h3>四、部署与优化</h3>\n\n<p>项目部署时需要注意：</p>\n\n<ul>\n    <li>使用Docker容器化部署，简化环境配置</li>\n    <li>配置Nginx反向代理，提高访问性能</li>\n    <li>实现静态资源CDN加速</li>\n    <li>数据库定期备份策略</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://enumerate-oss.oss-cn-qingdao.aliyuncs.com/15e8a303-4ba9-4c7d-8f9a-661ffd66c6ff.jpeg\" alt=\"编程开发图片\"></p>\n\n<p>通过以上步骤，我们可以构建一个功能完善、性能优良的个人博客系统。当然，实际开发过程中还会遇到各种问题，需要不断学习和优化。</p>\n\n<p>更多技术细节，可以参考我的GitHub仓库：<a href=\"https://github.com/example/blog-system\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/example/blog-system</a></p>','[\'前端\']',0,'vue3 and java springboot 个人博客'),(5,'配置阿里OSS','寄术笔记','2025-11-30 22:42:44','1',0,0,'https://tse4.mm.bing.net/th/id/OIP.ERgUW7_4qTLs90pmsPUOzgHaFv?rs=1&pid=ImgDetMain&o=7&rm=3','<h2>阿里OSS对象存储 Java配置</h2>\n<p>这废物阿里OSS对象配置每次都得翻官方文档，写的是又冗长又看不懂，今天哥们写个自己一看就能看懂的自用教程吧=v=。</p>\n<h3>环境变量设置</h3>\n<p>先弄个废物环境变量，让Java能读到你的敏感信息。</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-cmd\">setx OSS_ACCESS_KEY_ID \"YOUR_ACCESS_KEY_ID\"\nsetx OSS_ACCESS_KEY_SECRET \"YOUR_ACCESS_KEY_SECRET\"</code></pre>\n<h3>配置依赖</h3>\n<p>官方说Java7以上能用。先配置maven，其他我不会。</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">&lt;dependency&gt;\n    &lt;groupId&gt;com.aliyun.oss&lt;/groupId&gt;\n    &lt;artifactId&gt;aliyun-sdk-oss&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n    &lt;version&gt;3.17.4&lt;/version&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;</code></pre>\n<p>如果使用的是Java 9及以上的版本，则需要添加以下JAXB相关依赖。(官网原话)</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">&lt;dependency&gt;\n    &lt;groupId&gt;javax.xml.bind&lt;/groupId&gt;\n    &lt;artifactId&gt;jaxb-api&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n    &lt;version&gt;2.3.1&lt;/version&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;\n&lt;dependency&gt;\n    &lt;groupId&gt;javax.activation&lt;/groupId&gt;\n    &lt;artifactId&gt;activation&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n    &lt;version&gt;1.1.1&lt;/version&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;\n&lt;!-- no more than 2.3.3--&gt;\n&lt;dependency&gt;\n    &lt;groupId&gt;org.glassfish.jaxb&lt;/groupId&gt;\n    &lt;artifactId&gt;jaxb-runtime&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n    &lt;version&gt;2.3.3&lt;/version&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;</code></pre>\n<h3>配置你的敏感信息</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-properties\"># 阿里云OSS配置\naliyun.oss.endpoint=oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com\naliyun.oss.access-key-id=your-access-key-id\naliyun.oss.access-key-secret=your-access-key-secret\naliyun.oss.bucket-name=your-bucket-name\n# 文件上传大小限制（可选）\nspring.servlet.multipart.max-file-size=10MB\nspring.servlet.multipart.max-request-size=50MB</code></pre>\n<h3>整个配置类</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-java\">import com.aliyun.oss.OSS;\nimport com.aliyun.oss.OSSClientBuilder;\nimport org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Value;\nimport org.springframework.context.annotation.Bean;\nimport org.springframework.context.annotation.Configuration;\n\n@Configuration\npublic class OSSConfig {\n\n    @Value(\"${aliyun.oss.endpoint}\")\n    private String endpoint;\n\n    @Value(\"${aliyun.oss.access-key-id}\")\n    private String accessKeyId;\n\n    @Value(\"${aliyun.oss.access-key-secret}\")\n    private String accessKeySecret;\n\n    @Bean\n    public OSS ossClient() {\n        return new OSSClientBuilder().build(endpoint, accessKeyId, accessKeySecret);\n    }\n}</code></pre>\n<h3>整个工具类</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-java\">import com.aliyun.oss.OSS;\nimport com.aliyun.oss.model.*;\nimport org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Value;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Component;\nimport org.springframework.web.multipart.MultipartFile;\n\nimport java.io.IOException;\nimport java.io.InputStream;\nimport java.util.UUID;\n\n@Component\npublic class OSSUtil {\n\n    @Value(\"${aliyun.oss.bucket-name}\")\n    private String bucketName;\n\n    private final OSS ossClient;\n\n    // 构造注入OSS客户端\n    public OSSUtil(OSS ossClient) {\n        this.ossClient = ossClient;\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * 上传文件到OSS\n     * @param file 上传的文件\n     * @return 文件访问URL\n     */\n    public String uploadFile(MultipartFile file) throws IOException {\n        // 生成唯一文件名（避免覆盖）\n        String originalFilename = file.getOriginalFilename();\n        String fileName = UUID.randomUUID().toString() + \n                          originalFilename.substring(originalFilename.lastIndexOf(\".\"));\n        \n        // 获取文件输入流\n        InputStream inputStream = file.getInputStream();\n        \n        // 设置文件元信息\n        ObjectMetadata metadata = new ObjectMetadata();\n        metadata.setContentType(file.getContentType());\n        \n        // 上传文件\n        ossClient.putObject(bucketName, fileName, inputStream, metadata);\n        \n        // 返回文件访问URL\n        return \"https://\" + bucketName + \".\" + ossClient.getEndpoint().getHost() + \"/\" + fileName;\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * 下载OSS文件\n     * @param objectName OSS中的文件名\n     * @return 文件输入流\n     */\n    public InputStream downloadFile(String objectName) {\n        OSSObject ossObject = ossClient.getObject(bucketName, objectName);\n        return ossObject.getObjectContent();\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * 删除OSS文件\n     * @param objectName OSS中的文件名\n     */\n    public void deleteFile(String objectName) {\n        ossClient.deleteObject(bucketName, objectName);\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * 判断文件是否存在\n     * @param objectName OSS中的文件名\n     * @return 是否存在\n     */\n    public boolean doesFileExist(String objectName) {\n        return ossClient.doesObjectExist(bucketName, objectName);\n    }\n}</code></pre>\n<h3>用一用</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-java\">import org.springframework.http.HttpStatus;\nimport org.springframework.http.ResponseEntity;\nimport org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.*;\nimport org.springframework.web.multipart.MultipartFile;\n\nimport java.io.IOException;\nimport java.util.HashMap;\nimport java.util.Map;\n\n@RestController\n@RequestMapping(\"/oss\")\npublic class OSSController {\n\n    private final OSSUtil ossUtil;\n\n    public OSSController(OSSUtil ossUtil) {\n        this.ossUtil = ossUtil;\n    }\n\n    @PostMapping(\"/upload\")\n    public ResponseEntity&lt;Map&lt;String, String&gt;&gt; uploadFile(@RequestParam(\"file\") MultipartFile file) {\n        try {\n            String fileUrl = ossUtil.uploadFile(file);\n            Map&lt;String, String&gt; result = new HashMap&lt;&gt;();\n            result.put(\"url\", fileUrl);\n            result.put(\"message\", \"文件上传成功\");\n            return ResponseEntity.ok(result);\n        } catch (IOException e) {\n            Map&lt;String, String&gt; error = new HashMap&lt;&gt;();\n            error.put(\"message\", \"文件上传失败：\" + e.getMessage());\n            return ResponseEntity.status(HttpStatus.INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR).body(error);\n        }\n    }\n\n    @DeleteMapping(\"/delete/{fileName}\")\n    public ResponseEntity&lt;Map&lt;String, String&gt;&gt; deleteFile(@PathVariable String fileName) {\n        try {\n            ossUtil.deleteFile(fileName);\n            Map&lt;String, String&gt; result = new HashMap&lt;&gt;();\n            result.put(\"message\", \"文件删除成功\");\n            return ResponseEntity.ok(result);\n        } catch (Exception e) {\n            Map&lt;String, String&gt; error = new HashMap&lt;&gt;();\n            error.put(\"message\", \"文件删除失败：\" + e.getMessage());\n            return ResponseEntity.status(HttpStatus.INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR).body(error);\n        }\n    }\n}</code></pre>\n<p>结束。</p>','[\'java\',\'springboot\']',0,'这废物阿里OSS对象配置每次都得翻官方文档，写的是又冗长又看不懂，今天哥们写个自己一看就能看懂的自用教程吧=v=。'),(6,'如何简单进行分页查询','寄术笔记','2025-12-01 13:17:08','1',0,0,'https://ts4.tc.mm.bing.net/th/id/OIP-C.SCN14IfvWrq4gnVncSeKBgHaE7?rs=1&pid=ImgDetMain&o=7&rm=3','<h2>分页mybatisplus实现</h2>\n\n<p>作为crud（n.脏东西；污垢；渣滓）（不是）之一的R Retrieve(查询)。分页查询是必然大量面对的，现在有不少分页插件，此次拿mybatisplus 和 page helper 来个小教程。</p>\n\n<h3>一、mybatisplus 实现</h3>\n\n<p>前端用的时候只需要传参 pageNum 当前页面 pageSize 一页有多少</p>\n\n<h4>Controller层</h4>\n\n<pre><code class=\"language-java\">@CrossOrigin\n@GetMapping(\"/list\")\npublic Result&lt;Page&lt;Article&gt;&gt; list(\n        @RequestParam(defaultValue = \"1\") Integer pageNum,\n        @RequestParam(defaultValue = \"4\") Integer pageSize) {\n\n    log.info(\"获取文章列表，分页参数：页码{}，每页条数{}\", pageNum, pageSize);\n    // 创建分页对象\n    Page&lt;Article&gt; page = new Page&lt;&gt;(pageNum, pageSize);\n    // 调用Service的分页查询方法\n    Page&lt;Article&gt; articlePage = articleService.page(page);\n\n    return Result.success(articlePage);\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<h4>Service层</h4>\n\n<pre><code class=\"language-java\">public Page&lt;Article&gt; page(Page&lt;Article&gt; page) {\n    // 方式1：使用MyBatis-Plus的mapper分页\n    return articleMapper.selectPage(page, null);\n\n    // 方式2：自定义SQL分页（如果需要复杂条件）\n    // return page.setRecords(articleMapper.selectArticlePage(page));\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<h3>二、PageHelper实现</h3>\n\n<p>这里拿我之前苍穹外卖例子来吧</p>\n\n<h4>Controller层</h4>\n\n<pre><code class=\"language-java\">@GetMapping(\"/page\")\npublic Result&lt;PageResult&gt; page(DishPageQueryDTO dishPageQueryDTO) {\n    log.info(\"分页查询菜品{}\", dishPageQueryDTO);\n    PageResult res = dishService.page(dishPageQueryDTO);\n    return Result.success(res);\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<h4>Service层</h4>\n\n<p>这是经典三板斧，分页参数 强转 构造返回对象，mapper的page方法就是全部查询，pagehelper自己去拦截，去修改sql语句，基本上所有分页插件都是这么实现的。</p>\n\n<pre><code class=\"language-java\">public PageResult page(DishPageQueryDTO dishPageQueryDTO) {\n    //1 设置分页参数\n    int page = dishPageQueryDTO.getPage();\n    int pageSize = dishPageQueryDTO.getPageSize();\n    PageHelper.startPage(page, pageSize);\n\n    //2 查询并强转\n    Page&lt;DishVO&gt; res = (Page&lt;DishVO&gt;)dishMapper.page(dishPageQueryDTO);\n\n    //3 构造返回对象\n    return PageResult.builder()\n            .total(res.getTotal())\n            .records(res.getResult())\n            .build();\n}\n</code></pre>','[\'java\',\'springboot\']',0,'作为crud（n.脏东西；污垢；渣滓）（不是）之一的R Retrieve(查询)。分页查询是必然大量面对的，现在有不少分页插件，此次拿mybatisplus 和 page helper 来个小教程。');
